v 3
d wordcloud2: Interactive word cloud generator for Stata
d
d Author: Fahad Mirza
d Support: https://github.com/fahad-mirza/wordcloud2_stata/issues
d
d wordcloud2 reads a string variable containing free text, counts word
d frequencies across all observations, and renders the results as a
d fully interactive, self-contained HTML/SVG word cloud. Words are
d sized proportionally to their frequency and placed using a
d collision-free Archimedean spiral layout algorithm.
d
d Requires: Stata 15 or later
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260222
d Version: 1.2.0 (Beta)
d
f wordcloud2.ado
f wordcloud2.sthlp
f wordcloud2_example.do
e
